            <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_150gc' title='Col. 150GC &mdash; HL Deb 03 June 2003 vol 648 c150GC' name='column_150gc' href='#column_150gc' rel='bookmark'>150GC</a>
            it would have been a scandal if they had been extradited. Again, surely they would have been protected by dual criminality.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0648P0-05167'>
        <a name='S5LV0648P0_20030603_GCR_63'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-christopher-bathurst' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
